                <%= tt('Test mode: live Paymob payments are not yet enabled. Continuing simulates a successful payment for testing.', 'Test mode: live Paymob payments are not yet enabled. Continuing simulates a successful payment for testing.', 'وضع الاختبار: مدفوعات Paymob الحية غير مفعّلة بعد. المتابعة تحاكي عملية ناجحة للاختبار.') %>
